flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B[Build or refresh Core DB]
    B --> C[Apply core_kpi_views.sql]
    C --> D[Apply mart_dashboard_views.sql]
    D --> E[Run build_dashboard_cache.py]
    E --> F{Required mart views available?}
    F -- No --> G[Fail with actionable error]
    F -- Yes --> H[Drop old dash_cache_* tables]
    H --> I[Create latest platform quality cache table]
    I --> J[Create latest price deviation cache table]
    J --> K[Create 24h Binance price curve cache table]
    K --> L[Create symbol list cache table]
    L --> M[Create refresh metadata table]
    M --> N[Create cache indexes]
    N --> O[Commit transaction]
    O --> P([Dashboard cache ready])
    G --> Q([End with error])
